<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Email Verification</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f9fafb;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 16px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 24px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.10), 0 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
            text-align: center;
            border: 2px solid #3B82F6;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .container::before {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            top: -60px;
            left: -60px;
            width: 180px;
            height: 180px;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at 60px 60px, #3B82F6 0%, #f9fafb 100%);
            opacity: 0.12;
            z-index: 0;
        }

        .container::after {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -60px;
            right: -60px;
            width: 180px;
            height: 180px;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at 120px 120px, #3B82F6 0%, #f9fafb 100%);
            opacity: 0.10;
            z-index: 0;
        }

        .logo {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #3B82F6;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        h2 {
            color: #1e293b;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        p {
            color: #334155;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 14px 32px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #3B82F6 0%, #6366F1 100%);
            color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-top: 24px;
            word-break: break-word;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.15);
            transition: background 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .button:hover {
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #2563eb 0%, #7c3aed 100%);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 18px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.22);
        }

        .footer {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #9ca3af;
            margin-top: 30px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                max-width: 100% !important;
                margin: 10px;
                padding: 16px !important;
                border-radius: 0 !important;
                box-shadow: none !important;
            }

            .logo {
                font-size: 20px !important;
            }

            h2 {
                font-size: 20px !important;
            }

            .button {
                width: 100% !important;
                padding: 16px 0 !important;
                font-size: 16px !important;
            }

            p,
            .footer {
                font-size: 15px !important;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="logo">ðŸŽ¨ ArtsyCraftsy</div>
        <h2>Verify Your Email Address</h2>
        <p>Hi <%= name %>,</p>
        <p>Thank you for signing up for ArtsyCraftsy! To complete your registration, please verify your email address by
            clicking the button below:</p>
        <a href="<%= redirectUrl %>" class="button" style="color: #fff;">Verify Email</a>
        <p>If the button doesnâ€™t work, you can also copy and paste the following link into your browser:</p>
        <p style="word-break: break-all;"><a href="<%= redirectUrl %>">
                <%= redirectUrl %>
            </a></p>
        <div class="footer">
            If you didnâ€™t create an account, you can safely ignore this email.<br />
            &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> ArtsyCraftsy. All rights reserved.
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>